首先藍店內食客比例上黃嘅一定少啲，係有機會誤中，而你食得藍店越多中嘅機會越高係一個比食客嘅cost，佢地自然會減少去食。（有人話食一半黃藍店都叫黃，最多叫誤中中立）<br />\n<br />\n建議：效法裝修訂立規則，對唔同程度嘅藍店食客做出唔同嘅行為，而初期請唔好對相中人有咩行動，大家最想係佢地下次唔食，以宣傳為主。到傳遍黃絲光譜知道有類似行動，可以搵某啲日子集中針對某啲店舖，加強效果，最佳目標係成功搞掂一兩間有名藍店。"},{"pid":"1aba3657ffaca204046662dd6d669e8a7fd86c4e","tid":1822213,"uid":66368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T20:54:18.000Z","msg":"【Twitter戰線少左人⋯⋯】世界咁亂，但歐美仍幾乎日日報香港，手足請唔好放棄國際線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61d84990dfb5aa33bb8dbe6fadfa743f39ab8649","tid":1822213,"uid":66368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T20:57:44.000Z","msg":"由今日開始 吹雞去1.19大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1821322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1821322</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd285e13f1fb280458684b3b2bf82a965f87fd2f","tid":1822213,"uid":66368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:00:53.000Z","msg":"有人話自稱深黃嘅上前線都照食藍店，唔好搞批鬥<br />\n<br />\n如果真係深黃，你會覺得影相嘅人就令佢變藍變豬，而唔係反省同被提醒返半年幾受嘅苦？"},{"pid":"a8bf59435c556e184d7e29e3dbc1083e49167434","tid":1822213,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T23:11:24.000Z","msg":"係，  平台期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">台灣就公投完啦 甘香港人呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n一人一票<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香</span><span style=\"color: green;\">港</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">地</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">投</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">票</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港地投票 ~ 一個香港人的投票應用程式</span><br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=1b7503f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1\" data-auto